This is coding channel. The artist's channel here: https://www.livecoding.tv/tetianna

You control two wizards in this game. Wizards are not enough good in magic: they can't conjure fireballs nor teleporters nor even boxes. However, they are too proud for hiking. They use a combination of two artifacts for teleportation: a crystal ball a and magic cup (you need to put the ball to the cup). This pair can teleport our characters, but in the limited distance (to the next level). As a result, you need to combine the artefacts again and again many times. And sometimes it's not really easy to do.

https://www.livecoding.tv/tetianna

В игре вам предстоит управлять двумя волшебниками. Волшебники они, на самом деле, посредственные: фаерболы не умеют, телепорты не умеют и даже ящики из воздуха создавать не могут.
